Template:Hasdialogue/doc:
The &lt;nowiki>{{hasdialogue}}&lt;/nowiki> template is used to indicate and link to a dialogue page for any given article.
==Usage==
&lt;pre>
{{hasdialogue}}
{{hasdialogue|&lt;type>}}
{{hasdialogue|&lt;type>|&lt;link>}}
&lt;/pre>

'''Parameters:'''
*'''type''' - Optional (required if specifying link).  One of &lt;nowiki>{article, npc, familiar, quest}&lt;/nowiki>.  These options may be expanded in the future.
*'''link''' - Optional.  If the dialogue page is not found at &lt;nowiki>{{FULLPAGENAME}}/dialogue&lt;/nowiki> (which should only be the case in exceptional circumstances), used in place of the default link.  

==Examples==
&lt;pre>{{hasdialogue}}&lt;/pre> produces:
{{hasdialogue}}

&lt;pre>{{hasdialogue|npc}}&lt;/pre> produces:
{{hasdialogue|npc}}

&lt;pre>{{hasdialogue|article}}&lt;/pre> produces:
{{hasdialogue|article}}

&lt;pre>{{hasdialogue|familiar}}&lt;/pre> produces:
{{hasdialogue|familiar}}

&lt;pre>{{hasdialogue|quest}}&lt;/pre> produces:
{{hasdialogue|quest}}

&lt;pre>{{hasdialogue|quest|RuneScape:Yew grove}}&lt;/pre> produces:
{{hasdialogue|quest|RuneScape:Yew grove}}

&lt;noinclude>[[Category:Template documentation|{{PAGENAME}}]]&lt;/noinclude>

